org.at4j.zip

Class ZipEntryLocalFileHeaderData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.at4j.zip.ZipEntryLocalFileHeaderData

  • public class ZipEntryLocalFileHeaderData
extends Object
    This contains the subset of data from the local file header that cannot be found in the Zip entry's central directory record.

    This is part of the ZipFile implementations. Clients should not have to bother with this object.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Karl Gustafsson
